                    "content": "<ul><li>After cleansing, pour or pump a moderate amount into your hands.<br/></li><li>Gently pat over dry or slightly damp skin until foam activates.<br/></li><li>Leave on for about 30–60 seconds, then follow with your next skincare steps.</li></ul><p>Tip: Start by using this toner 2-3 times a week and increase frequency only as your skin tolerates it. Always layer a hydrating toner or serum afterward to buffer the Retinoid effect.<br/><br/></p>",
